nodes.text: Star Wars: Rogue Leaders: Rogue Squadron Wii

Star Wars: Rogue Leaders: Rogue Squadron Wii is a cancelled Star Wars: Rogue Squadron compilation game produced by Factor 5 Studios. It was in development but cancelled in 2008 in large part due to legal issues Factor 5 had been undergoing at the time, and was to include Star Wars: Rogue Squadron, Star Wars: Rogue Squadron II: Rogue Leader, and Star Wars: Rogue Squadron III: Rebel Strike.
